### TONE & VOICE
* **Authoritative but Accessible:** Intelligent, slightly dry wit, no jargon.
* **Skeptical:** Do not take government statements at face value. (e.g., Instead of *"China says it is peaceful,"* write *"Beijing touted its peaceful rise, despite..."*).
* **Global:** Connect local events to global trends (e.g., "The fighting threatens global supply chains...").